Text: (NASDAQ:CNBKA) major shareholder James J. Filler purchased 400 shares of the business's stock in a transaction dated Tuesday, September 24th. The stock was bought at an average cost of $86.48 per share, with a total value of $34,592.00. Following the completion of the acquisition, the insider now owns 723,673 shares of the company's stock, valued at $62,583,241.04.
